title: Kubernetes: Pod Restarts
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This service monitors the number of restarts of the underlying
 containers in the pod. The service reports the total number of
 restarts as well as the restart rate during the last hour.

 Upper levels for {WARN}/{CRIT} can be defined for both restart
 count and restart rate. No levels are set by default.

discovery:
 One service is created for a Pod.
